{{! ----------------------------------------------------------------- }}

<h3>Webpack</h3>

<p>Install Huebee with npm.</p>

``` bash
npm install huebee
```

<p>You can then <code>require('huebee')</code>.</p>

``` js
// main.js
var Huebee = require('huebee');

var hueb = new Huebee( '.color-input', {
  // options
});
```

<p>Run webpack.</p>

``` bash
webpack main.js bundle.js
```

{{! ----------------------------------------------------------------- }}

<h3>RequireJS</h3>

<p>You can require <code>huebee.pkgd.js</code>.</p>

``` js
requirejs( [
  'path/to/huebee.pkgd.js',
], function( Huebee ) {
  var hueb = new Huebee( '.color-input', {
    // options
  });
});
```

